# Demos

Flame Graph demos from the talk "Blazing Performance with Flame Graphs" (USENIX/LISA 2013), plus MySQL EXPLAIN demos for this project.

## MySQL EXPLAIN demos (`mysql-query-*.svg`)

Flame graph, bar chart, treemap, and diagram examples from `EXPLAIN ANALYZE FORMAT=JSON`. See the [main README](../README.md) for how to generate them.

## Viewing

These SVGs cannot be viewed on GitHub directly (inline script is blocked). Clone or download the repo and open them in a browser (`file://...`), or use the [docs index](https://vgrippa.github.io/myflames/) on GitHub Pages.
